# Never ship local state into the build context — keeps the build fast and the
# image clean, and avoids leaking local config.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/out
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
.git
.gitignore
*.md
.claude
.skill-extract
**/.env*
Dockerfile
.dockerignore

# …but these prebuilt outputs ARE needed by the Docker images (last match wins,
# so these negations must come after the broad ignores above).
!apps/web/out
!apps/web/out/**
!apps/web/.next
!apps/web/.next/standalone
!apps/web/.next/standalone/**
!apps/web/.next/static
!apps/web/.next/static/**
